OL,3,CBarry John: 'One of the greatest
OL,4,Csportsmen'
OL,6,F"A one off" and "gifted player" - just
OL,7,Fsome of the words used to describe
OL,8,FWales rugby great Barry John, who has .
OL,10,FThe former and British and Irish Lions
OL,11,Fdied peacefully in hospital, his
OL,12,Ffamily announced on Sunday 4 February.
OL,14,FJohn, who was nicknamed "The King" by
OL,15,FNew Zealand journalists after he
OL,16,Finspired the Lions' famous 1971 Test
OL,17,Fseries victory over the All Blacks,
OL,18,Fwon 25 Wales caps between 1966 and
OL,19,F1972.
