OL,6,F"There were no two people like him, he
OL,7,Fshowed he was very different." He
OL,8,Fcontinued.
OL,10,F"It was a pleasure to have called him
OL,11,Fa friend."
OL,13,FMr Ellis added: "Barry's name will
OL,14,Fnever be forgotten in the village and
OL,15,Fin the whole valley."
OL,17,F'A one-off'
OL,19,FDelme Thomas played with Barry John
OL,20,Ffor Llanelli RFC, Wales and the
OL,21,FBritish Lions.
