OL,6,FFellow British Lion, and president of
OL,7,Fthe WRU, played tribute to "The King".
OL,8,FTerry Cobner described him as "one of
OL,9,Fthe greatest sportsmen ever produced
OL,10,Fin Wales."
OL,12,FCobner played in the Welsh back-row
OL,13,Fand toured with the Lions in 1977. "He
OL,14,Fwas a glider, rather than a
OL,15,Fsidestepper, who had a subtle change
OL,16,Fof pace and direction.
OL,18,F"Coming on top of the recent deaths of
OL,19,FBrian Price and JPR Williams, this is
OL,20,Fanother huge blow for Welsh rugby", he
OL,21,Fsaid.
